#  command-line-args distinctive features:
#    - OPTION-DEFINITION-ARRAY pattern — flat array of plain
#      objects (no class hierarchies, no decorators, no Zod
#      schemas); each object is a self-describing flag spec
#    - JS CONSTRUCTOR AS TYPE — `type: String/Number/Boolean`
